  "content": [
    {
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "chapterTitle": "引言",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "26357890_6_447-812",
          "range": "447-812",
          "rangeStart": 447,
          "rangeEnd": 812,
          "markText": "谁都不是一座岛屿，自成一体；每个人都\n是欧洲大陆的一小块，那本土的一部\n分；如果一块泥巴被海浪冲掉，欧洲\n就小了一点，如果一座海岬，如果\n你朋友或你自己的庄园被冲掉，\n也是如此；任何人的死亡使我\n有所缺损，因为我与人类难\n解难分；所以千万不必去\n打听丧钟为谁而鸣；\n丧钟为你而鸣。",
          "colorStyle": 2,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1732704837,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2024-11-27 18:53:57",
          "chapterUid": 6,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26357890&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=447&rangeEnd=812",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/4a032ea0719230824a0d3d5?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=447&rangeEnd=812"
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
