      "range": "3451-3472",
      "markText": "“太阳一升起，悲哀就消散。悲哀就像迷雾。”",
      "totalCount": 64,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26357890&chapterUid=16&rangeStart=3451&rangeEnd=3472",
