    {
      "bookmarkId": "26357890_8_18841-18878",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "18841-18878",
      "markText": "快活活的情绪要好得多，而且这也是一种吉兆。仿佛你还活着的时候就得到了永生。",
      "totalCount": 48,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26357890&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=18841&rangeEnd=18878",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/4a032ea0719230824a0d3d5?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=18841&rangeEnd=18878"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "26357890_10_7227-7240",
      "chapterUid": 10,
      "range": "7227-7240",
      "markText": "把他们杀了并不能给他们教训",
      "totalCount": 48,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26357890&chapterUid=10&rangeStart=7227&rangeEnd=7240",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/4a032ea0719230824a0d3d5?chapterUid=10&rangeStart=7227&rangeEnd=7240"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "26357890_16_7951-8006",
      "chapterUid": 16,
      "range": "7951-8006",
      "markText": "“你从来没妈，”比拉尔对他说。这些骂人话在形式上达到了操西班牙语骂人的极点，所表达的行为从不明说而只作暗示。",
      "totalCount": 36,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26357890&chapterUid=16&rangeStart=7951&rangeEnd=8006",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/4a032ea0719230824a0d3d5?chapterUid=16&rangeStart=7951&rangeEnd=8006"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "26357890_17_19545-19594",
      "chapterUid": 17,
      "range": "19545-19594",
      "markText": "就在这时，我知道这两排人起了杀性，而使他们变成这模样的，先是堂里卡多的辱骂，后是堂福斯蒂诺的胆怯。",
      "totalCount": 36,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26357890&chapterUid=17&rangeStart=19545&rangeEnd=19594",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/4a032ea0719230824a0d3d5?chapterUid=17&rangeStart=19545&rangeEnd=19594"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "26357890_8_8841-8858",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "8841-8858",
      "markText": "我决不思考。别打算引诱我去思考。”",
      "totalCount": 34,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26357890&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=8841&rangeEnd=8858",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/4a032ea0719230824a0d3d5?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=8841&rangeEnd=8858"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "26357890_20_11216-11295",
      "chapterUid": 20,
      "range": "11216-11295",
      "markText": "接着，在这样一场糟糕的把戏中，设法取得两帮微不足道的游击队的配合，在几乎不可能的情况下帮你炸桥，来阻止一场也许已经开始的反攻，这时你却遇见了玛丽亚这样的姑娘。",
      "totalCount": 34,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26357890&chapterUid=20&rangeStart=11216&rangeEnd=11295",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/4a032ea0719230824a0d3d5?chapterUid=20&rangeStart=11216&rangeEnd=11295"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "26357890_24_2360-2378",
      "chapterUid": 24,
      "range": "2360-2378",
      "markText": "人家卑劣，可并不能使你的卑劣变得正当",
      "totalCount": 34,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26357890&chapterUid=24&rangeStart=2360&rangeEnd=2378",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/4a032ea0719230824a0d3d5?chapterUid=24&rangeStart=2360&rangeEnd=2378"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "26357890_50_40190-40265",
      "chapterUid": 50,
      "range": "40190-40265",
      "markText": "？宗教使人们得到很大的安慰，然而我们知道，实在也没有什么可怕的。糟的只是缺乏信念罢了。只有当死亡拖延很久才来临，并且痛苦得使你丢人的时候，这才是糟的。",
      "totalCount": 34,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26357890&chapterUid=50&rangeStart=40190&rangeEnd=40265",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/4a032ea0719230824a0d3d5?chapterUid=50&rangeStart=40190&rangeEnd=40265"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "26357890_37_2724-2748",
      "chapterUid": 37,
      "range": "2724-2748",
      "markText": "内战后祖父在卡尼堡的时候，印第安人经常剥人头皮。",
      "totalCount": 32,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26357890&chapterUid=37&rangeStart=2724&rangeEnd=2748",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/4a032ea0719230824a0d3d5?chapterUid=37&rangeStart=2724&rangeEnd=2748"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "26357890_8_9477-9501",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "9477-9501",
      "markText": "不能发愁。发愁和恐惧一样糟糕。只会使事情更难办。",
      "totalCount": 30,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26357890&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=9477&rangeEnd=9501",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/4a032ea0719230824a0d3d5?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=9477&rangeEnd=9501"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "26357890_20_10285-10328",
      "chapterUid": 20,
      "range": "10285-10328",
      "markText": "我爱她之深使我觉得自己确实要死过去似的，而我过去从来不相信会这样，也不认为会有这种事。",
      "totalCount": 30,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26357890&chapterUid=20&rangeStart=10285&rangeEnd=10328",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/4a032ea0719230824a0d3d5?chapterUid=20&rangeStart=10285&rangeEnd=10328"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "26357890_23_14576-14631",
      "chapterUid": 23,
      "range": "14576-14631",
      "markText": "“我要离开这儿，”奥古斯丁说。“没错，人家说我们这辈子得听一吨废话，可刚才这会儿我每只耳朵就灌进了二十五磅。”",
      "totalCount": 30,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26357890&chapterUid=23&rangeStart=14576&rangeEnd=14631",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/4a032ea0719230824a0d3d5?chapterUid=23&rangeStart=14576&rangeEnd=14631"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "26357890_30_6423-6500",
      "chapterUid": 30,
      "range": "6423-6500",
      "markText": "但愿我们打赢这场战争，一个人也不枪毙，”安塞尔莫说。“但愿我们公正地治理国家，出一分力量的都得一分好处，大家有福共享。让反对过我们的人受教育，好认识错误。",
      "totalCount": 28,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26357890&chapterUid=30&rangeStart=6423&rangeEnd=6500",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/4a032ea0719230824a0d3d5?chapterUid=30&rangeStart=6423&rangeEnd=6500"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "26357890_37_7715-7737",
      "chapterUid": 37,
      "range": "7715-7737",
      "markText": "能确信就好办得多，他想。能确信总是好办得多。",
      "totalCount": 28,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26357890&chapterUid=37&rangeStart=7715&rangeEnd=7737",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/4a032ea0719230824a0d3d5?chapterUid=37&rangeStart=7715&rangeEnd=7737"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "26357890_37_1666-1719",
      "chapterUid": 37,
      "range": "1666-1719",
      "markText": "别接着欺骗自己，以为可以不必炸桥。总有一天你得把它炸掉，要不，另炸一座。换句话说，不是这座桥，就是另一座。",
      "totalCount": 26,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26357890&chapterUid=37&rangeStart=1666&rangeEnd=1719",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/4a032ea0719230824a0d3d5?chapterUid=37&rangeStart=1666&rangeEnd=1719"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "26357890_17_30363-30443",
      "chapterUid": 17,
      "range": "30363-30443",
      "markText": "我们镇上杀掉法西斯分子的经过就这么结束了，幸亏后面的情形我没见到，要不是有了那个醉汉，我准能全部看到。所以他倒做了件好事，因为镇公所里的惨状，看了会叫人难受的。",
      "totalCount": 24,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26357890&chapterUid=17&rangeStart=30363&rangeEnd=30443",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/4a032ea0719230824a0d3d5?chapterUid=17&rangeStart=30363&rangeEnd=30443"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "26357890_21_13922-13981",
      "chapterUid": 21,
      "range": "13922-13981",
      "markText": "但是她现在知道，公牛的劲头、公牛的勇气都不能持久，那么什么能持久呢？我持久，她想。是呀，我坚持下来了。可是为了什么呢？",
      "totalCount": 24,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26357890&chapterUid=21&rangeStart=13922&rangeEnd=13981",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/4a032ea0719230824a0d3d5?chapterUid=21&rangeStart=13922&rangeEnd=13981"
    },
